.accordion#scenariosAccordion
  .accordion-item
    %h2.accordion-header
      %button.accordion-button.collapsed{type: 'button', data: {bs_toggle: 'collapse', bs_target: '#scenariosBody'}, aria: {expanded: 'false', controls: 'scenariosBody'}}
        Scenarios
    #scenariosBody.accordion-collapse.collapse
      .accordion-body
        %h3 Alert on Error Spikes
        %p
          Example Goal: Receive an alert when more than 2% of rows in an import contain errors, as long as at least 20 rows are affected. This catches situations where a CSV was corrupted during export, or data was saved in an unexpected format.
        %ul
          %li Set Error count threshold (%) to 2
          %li Set Minimum error count threshold to 20
        %h3 Alert on Unexpected Row Count Changes
        %p
          Example Goal: Flag any import where the total number of records in any file changes by more than 10%, as long as the change is at least 5 records. This catches situations like a project being left off an import, or a data cleanup routine unexpectedly removing records.
        %ul
          %li Record count change threshold (%) to 10
          %li Set Minimum change count threshold to 5
